precis:
Amendment (SCHEDULE No. 912) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which sets
Maximum Residue Limits on the amount of the insecticide "AMITRAZ" that can
be detected either on or in pears and apples or in the liver or kidneys of
cattle and hogs.
